Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:14.89,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:15.14,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:18.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:23.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:26.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:30.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:33.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:36.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.71,0:00:40.17,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:44.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:48.35,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.35,0:00:50.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:54.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:59.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.36,0:01:03.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:11.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:15.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.39,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs125\bord0.5\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,210.389)}Deathmatch! The Ant-Eating
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.39,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(587.167,640.389)}Devil Arigabari
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.14,0:01:30.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mount Tengu,\Nin a corner of the Southern Alps.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.31,0:01:35.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Anyone who climbs this\Nmountain is never seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:42.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Those who live near it have begun\Nto give it another name: Mount Vanishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:43.68,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\3c&H559BA9&}Southern Alps\NEntrance to Mount Tengu\N{\c&H3B3CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Danger - Do Not Climb
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Feels great, huh?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's past here.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:02:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But, for those with an adventurous spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:03.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mount Tengu has another appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:05.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And here comes another pair of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:08.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,unaware that this mountain\Nis such an ominous place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.37,0:02:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The peak is just past this waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The fog's really rolling in, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.08,0:02:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.\N- Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.67,0:02:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamada! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounded like Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Look carefully, right in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster! What are you\Ndoing with Yamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to run a little test\Non your friend here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see if you can endure the bacteria\Nknown as "the Curse of the Amazon"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,which I, the great Arigabari, spread!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:07.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An anteater monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:12.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It is a cyborg smuggled by Shocker\Nto Japan from the remote Amazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:17.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The anteater monster carries a bacteria\Nknown as "the Curse of the Amazon"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.97,0:04:21.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,which it injects into the human body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll inject you with\Nmore of my bacteria!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.95,Italics,,0,0,0,,Wait, Arigabari.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:32.48,Italics,,0,0,0,,The man has endured\Nthe bacteria admirably.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:35.57,Italics,,0,0,0,,Assign him to spread the infection, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:40.47,Italics,,0,0,0,,This will allow the computer\Nto gather data on how useful it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Return him to good health,\Nand then use him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:50.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,Then I will show my\Npower through him, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Arigabari.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the Kamen Rider learns\Nof our plans and attempts to interfere,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:05:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you can defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Arigabari!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Descend from Mount Tengu to\Nthe village, and show your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall! This is the day\NI've been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:20.78,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\3c&H559BA9&}Southern Alps\NEntrance to Mount Tengu\N{\c&H3B3CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Danger - Do Not Climb
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna look for my big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even grown adults have climbed\Nup there, never to return! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without that, a kid like you\Nclimbing a mountain alone is suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right?\N- That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother is a\Nveteran mountain-climber.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he's gotten trapped, I know he's\Nstill alive, waiting for help to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But we've all been\Nsearching for three days,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and we still haven't found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true! He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamada wandered into the mist,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and died falling from a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to wait for the fog to clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:20.81,Italics,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.89,Italics,,0,0,0,,That's not my brother, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to worry you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just glad you're safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Izaki from the third floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I ask you a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Izaki, it's awfully late...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to serve Shocker, as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Izaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, you will serve me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say you're worrying too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't help feeling like\Nit's not really my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Adults say it all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A life-or-death experience\Ncan really change someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet getting stranded changed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You think he wouldn't even\Nlike the same foods, even?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Foods?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've been watching since\Nhe came down from the mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and he hasn't eaten a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what's he eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He sneaks out in\Nthe middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he's eating something then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a ghost story!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just one thing\Nthat's bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Since my brother came back,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,all the ants around the\Napartment have gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ants?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He says the ants are all gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The ants?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you taking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you using it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chairman...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't have it. I'm using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My savior! I owe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Goro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me to my apartment complex!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to help my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say no to you. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro and Hayato... they're peas in a pod!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.31,0:09:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be with you. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's heading for that\Nnew apartment complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's eating the ants!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.21,0:10:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, why are you eating ants?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I must continuously eat ants to cultivate\N"the Curse of the Amazon" bacteria
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,growing in my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"Curse of the Amazon"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna call Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Shocker cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do to my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother has become\Na Shocker guinea pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm using him to spread a\Nbacteria developed by Shocker
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,among the people of\Nthis apartment complex
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to spread destruction and havoc!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the story, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Exploiting an innocent man\Nto spread destruction...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's certainly clever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't let it go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:11:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come closer, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat him with the Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider is no match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:58.69,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll know one way or another\Nby the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No... don't die, Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor... please, take my blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy has suffered a\Ndeep psychological trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope the mental strain doesn't\Naffect his physical injuries, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mental strain?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not ready to be out of bed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll look after Goro. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're injured, too, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... he lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro... hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider will not lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He will beat that Shocker monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all... this is all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider is an idol...\Na hero to Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But he saw him defeated at the same\Ntime he himself was badly injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychological and\Nphysical injuries at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, I'm telling you...\Nthey're both sapping his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But right now, I just don't\Nthink I can beat Arigabari!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't grant the\Nwish of a single child,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,never talk to me again about justice,\Nor protecting humanity, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Can't" isn't allowed in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you such a gutless coward
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that one or two losses\Nhas you throwing in the towel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That nickname is only for my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No... let me say it, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, your words are the only thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether he pulls through or not will\Ncome down to his own strength of will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro. Stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,After all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't Kamen Rider come and see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,God...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Arigabari...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:16:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you give up, Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Don't let it beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll need more than this\Nto get past Arigabari's claws!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If it will save Goro, I'll gladly help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked out a new move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.06,0:18:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, go around that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all affected...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:49.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Arigabari had already been and gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:51.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,spreading "the Curse\Nof the Amazon" bacteria
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:54.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to the people of the apartment complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Izaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Izaki, speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:18:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Izaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, he got to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeo's brother originally\Nwent missing on Mount Tengu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If this all started on Mount Tengu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,then that must be where Shocker's base is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.27,0:19:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, you keep watch here.\NI'll head to Mount Tengu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! Keep fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't give up, do you, Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Arigabari...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Seize him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I will stop you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For Goro, and for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You no longer stand a chance against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll meet your end here on Mount Tengu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... you're helpless before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Manji Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.50,0:21:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I won... I finally won!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They left these antidote capsules\Nin their base on Mount Tengu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They should work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll get better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.01,0:22:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji... go see Goro. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:17.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The antidote worked, saving\Nthe people of the apartment complex
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.39,0:22:18.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,from Shocker's evil scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.31,0:22:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.21,0:22:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I defeated Arigabari.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.89,0:22:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to get better too, Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.06,0:22:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeo's brother has recovered as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.24,0:22:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.23,0:22:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, you need to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.41,0:22:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.44,0:22:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider really came!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.82,0:22:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean in a dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.01,0:22:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider really came\Nto tell me he beat the monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chairman... Goro's acting strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.79,0:23:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not strange at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.14,0:23:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider fought\Nfor Goro... and he won!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.13,0:23:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro, you gave Kamen Rider strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.14,0:23:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.30,0:23:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.13,0:23:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So... get better soon, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:27.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mount Tengu, a place once feared,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.25,0:23:29.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,would never be called\Nthe devil's mountain again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.66,0:23:33.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But evil organization Shocker\Nhasn't given up on Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:35.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Keep up the fight, our Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:41.04,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.02,0:23:43.86,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.02,0:23:45.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:47.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the man-eating flower, Dokudalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:49.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a monster that creates\Nextracts from poisonous flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.68,0:23:51.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When Mari and Yuri are captured,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:53.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato must infiltrate\Na Shocker base to save them,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.12,0:23:55.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but he falls into Colonel Zol's trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.68,0:23:57.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:24:01.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Man-Eating Flower, Dokudalian."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.39,0:24:01.02,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,200.389)}The Man-Eating Flower
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.39,0:24:01.02,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(567.167,680.389)}Dokudalian
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:10.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.42,0:24:13.42,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.42,0:24:15.38,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.38,0:24:18.43,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the villains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.93,0:24:20.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.80,0:24:22.68,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.68,0:24:24.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.47,0:24:25.92,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.27,0:24:28.31,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.36,0:24:34.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with all of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.03,0:24:37.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.61,0:24:41.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.70,0:24:45.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Deathmatch! The Ant-Eating Devil Arigabari